rlist: You may **__not__** use any form of communication to metagame.
Usernames that can not be tagged or contain vulgar or inappropriate language are not allowed.
Spamming any channel will result in a mute.
You may not distribute knowledge of exploits or bugs. There is no exception to this.
Be respectful to all members of the community. If you have an issue open a support ticket.
Advertising another server/community in any form, including DM's will result in a ban.
Try to keep your messages in their according channels.
The use of hacks is strictly prohibited and you will be banned if you are caught using or distributing them.
Do not hesitate to contact staff if you have a question. They are here to help you!
Have fun and enjoy your stay!
